            <details class="rounded-[24px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">Can I do this part-time?</summary>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Yes. The website and offers are positioned for people who want to build gradually while managing current responsibilities. The point is not to disrupt life, but to grow with structure.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="rounded-[24px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">Do I need experience?</summary>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Not necessarily. Some offers are designed specifically for beginners who need a clear starting point, guidance, and simple next steps.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="rounded-[24px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">How do payments work?</summary>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Depending on the offer, you either use a hosted checkout link, reserve your spot, or chat first on WhatsApp. The page is built to support both direct payment and assisted checkout guidance.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="rounded-[24px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">Which payment methods are accepted?</summary>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">The architecture supports M-Pesa, Tigo Pesa, Airtel Money, Halo Pesa, card, and bank transfer, depending on the final gateway setup and offer flow.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="rounded-[24px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">What happens after payment?</summary>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">You should receive confirmation, a next-step message, and either digital delivery details or onboarding guidance. This page explains that clearly to reduce uncertainty.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="rounded-[24px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">Do I need to chat first?</summary>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">No. For some offers, direct checkout is available. But many people prefer to chat first, and the page keeps that path visible because it is a natural buying behavior.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="rounded-[24px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">Is this beginner-friendly?</summary>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Yes. The tone, offer structure, and support paths are designed to reduce overwhelm, answer basic questions, and help people choose a reasonable next step.</p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-8 md:py-14">
        <div class="rounded-[34px] bg-panel p-6 text-white shadow-lift md:p-10">
          <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:items-center">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-white/60">Final Call To Action</p>
              <h2 class="mt-3 max-w-3xl font-display text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl">If you are ready to start, the next step should feel simple.</h2>
              <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-slate-200">
                Chat on WhatsApp for quick guidance. Call if you want direct clarity. Browse the offer catalog if you prefer to decide at your own pace. No pressure. Clear next steps.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-[28px] bg-white p-5 text-slate-900 shadow-soft">
              <div class="grid gap-3">
                <a
                  href="#"
                  data-wa-link
                  data-message="Habari Paul, niko tayari kuanza. Naomba uniongoze next step."
                  class="inline-flex min-h-[54px] items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-whatsapp px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-green-500"
                >
                  Chat on WhatsApp
                </a>
                <a href="#" data-call-link class="inline-flex min-h-[54px] items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-50">
                  Call Now
                </a>
                <a href="#offers" class="inline-flex min-h-[54px] items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-50">
                  Browse Offers
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Unsure where to begin? Start with WhatsApp and ask one simple question.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-200 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-8">
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-start">
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink">Paul Mwaikenda</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">
              Part-Time Business &amp; Entrepreneurs Coach |
              <a href="{{ config('brand.instagram_url') }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-semibold text-ink underline underline-offset-4">
                Instagram: {{ config('brand.instagram_handle') }}
              </a>
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-500">Support contact paths are built around WhatsApp first, with call and lead capture as secondary support routes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Paul Mwaikenda. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Independent distributor / coach notice: any offer, program, or partner arrangement should be clarified before payment.</p>
            <p>Results vary. This website does not make income guarantees.</p>
            <p>Payment note: hosted checkout links and API endpoints in this file are placeholders until production credentials are added.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <div id="checkoutModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-[70] hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/70" data-close-checkout></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 max-h-[90vh] overflow-y-auto rounded-t-[30px] bg-white p-5 shadow-lift md:bottom-4 md:right-4 md:left-auto md:top-4 md:w-[28rem] md:rounded-[30px]">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-slate-500">Checkout Summary</p>
            <h2 id="checkoutName" class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink">Offer Name</h2>
          </div>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-close-checkout
            class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-slate-600"
            aria-label="Close checkout summary"
          >
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M6 6l12 12M18 6L6 18"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5 space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-[24px] bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">Who it is for</p>
            <p id="checkoutFor" class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-[24px] bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">Format</p>
              <p id="checkoutFormat" class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-[24px] bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">Investment</p>
              <p id="checkoutPrice" class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink"></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[24px] bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">Clear outcome</p>
            <p id="checkoutOutcome" class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[24px] bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">Supported payment methods</p>
            <div id="checkoutMethods" class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[24px] border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900">Need help? Chat first.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-emerald-800">Secure checkout guidance, mobile money support, and clear next steps remain available even if you prefer to ask before paying.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[24px] bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">What happens next</p>
            <p id="checkoutNextSteps" class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600"></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-3">
          <button
            type="button"
            id="checkoutPrimary"
            class="inline-flex min-h-[54px] items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-accent px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-ink transition hover:bg-amber-300"
          >
            Continue
          </button>
          <a
            href="#"
            id="checkoutSupport"
            data-wa-link
            data-message="Habari Paul, ningependa msaada kabla ya kulipia."
            class="inline-flex min-h-[54px] items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-50"
          >
            Chat on WhatsApp Instead
          </a>
        </div>

        <div id="checkoutStatus" class="mt-4 hidden rounded-[20px] border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm leading-7 text-amber-900" aria-live="polite"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fixed inset-x-4 bottom-4 z-40 sm:hidden">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 rounded-[24px] border border-white/70 bg-white/95 p-3 shadow-lift backdrop-blur">
        <a
          href="#"
          data-wa-link
          data-message="Habari Paul, nimetoka kwenye website yako na nataka kuanza."
          class="inline-flex min-h-[54px] items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-whatsapp px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white"
        >
          WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a href="#" data-call-link class="inline-flex min-h-[54px] items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">
          Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="toast" class="pointer-events-none fixed left-1/2 top-5 z-[90] hidden -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-ink px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lift"></div>

    <script>
      /*
        Contact and payment setup now comes from Laravel config/brand.php and .env.
        Update BRAND_WHATSAPP_NUMBER, BRAND_PHONE_NUMBER, and PAYMENT_LINK_* values there.
      */
      const SITE_CONFIG = {{ \Illuminate\Support\Js::from($siteConfig) }};

      const state = {
        currentOffer: null
      };

      const menuToggle = document.getElementById("menuToggle");
      const mobileMenu = document.getElementById("mobileMenu");
      const toast = document.getElementById("toast");
      const modal = document.getElementById("checkoutModal");
      const checkoutStatus = document.getElementById("checkoutStatus");
      const checkoutPrimary = document.getElementById("checkoutPrimary");
      const checkoutSupport = document.getElementById("checkoutSupport");
      const leadInterest = document.getElementById("leadInterest");
      const leadForm = document.getElementById("leadForm");
      const leadState = document.getElementById("leadState");
      const leadSubmit = document.getElementById("leadSubmit");
      const leadName = document.getElementById("leadName");
      const leadEmail = document.getElementById("leadEmail");
      const nameError = document.getElementById("nameError");
      const emailError = document.getElementById("emailError");

      const isPlaceholder = (value) =>
        !value || /[A-Z_]{4,}/.test(value) || value.includes("PLACEHOLDER");

      const digitsOnly = (value) => (value || "").replace(/\D+/g, "");

      function showToast(message) {
        toast.textContent = message;
        toast.classList.remove("hidden");
        window.clearTimeout(showToast.timer);
        showToast.timer = window.setTimeout(() => {
          toast.classList.add("hidden");
        }, 2800);
      }

      function buildWhatsAppUrl(message) {
        const number = digitsOnly(SITE_CONFIG.whatsappNumber);
        if (!number || isPlaceholder(SITE_CONFIG.whatsappNumber)) return null;
        const text = encodeURIComponent(message || "Habari Paul, nimetoka kwenye website yako.");
        return "https://wa.me/" + number + "?text=" + text;
      }

      function buildCallUrl() {
        if (!SITE_CONFIG.phoneNumber || isPlaceholder(SITE_CONFIG.phoneNumber)) return null;
        return "tel:" + SITE_CONFIG.phoneNumber;
      }

      function wireContactLinks() {
        document.querySelectorAll("[data-wa-link]").forEach((link) => {
          const message = link.dataset.message || "Habari Paul, nimetoka kwenye website yako.";
          const url = buildWhatsAppUrl(message);

          if (url) {
            link.setAttribute("href", url);
            link.setAttribute("target", "_blank");
            link.setAttribute("rel", "noopener noreferrer");
          } else {
            link.setAttribute("href", "#");
            link.removeAttribute("target");
            link.removeAttribute("rel");
          }

          link.onclick = (event) => {
            const currentMessage = link.dataset.message || "Habari Paul, nimetoka kwenye website yako.";
            if (!buildWhatsAppUrl(currentMessage)) {
              event.preventDefault();
              showToast("WhatsApp is not configured yet. Add BRAND_WHATSAPP_NUMBER in .env.");
            }
          };
        });

        document.querySelectorAll("[data-call-link]").forEach((link) => {
          const url = buildCallUrl();
          if (url) {
            link.setAttribute("href", url);
          } else {
            link.setAttribute("href", "#");
          }

          link.onclick = (event) => {
            if (!buildCallUrl()) {
              event.preventDefault();
              showToast("Phone calling is not configured yet. Add BRAND_PHONE_NUMBER in .env.");
            }
          };
        });
      }

      function setMenu(open) {
        mobileMenu.classList.toggle("hidden", !open);
        menuToggle.setAttribute("aria-expanded", String(open));
      }

      menuToggle.addEventListener("click", () => {
        const open = menuToggle.getAttribute("aria-expanded") !== "true";
        setMenu(open);
      });

      mobileMenu.querySelectorAll("a").forEach((link) => {
        link.addEventListener("click", () => setMenu(false));
      });

      function openCheckout(offerData) {
        state.currentOffer = offerData;
        document.getElementById("checkoutName").textContent = offerData.name;
        document.getElementById("checkoutFor").textContent = offerData.for;
        document.getElementById("checkoutFormat").textContent = offerData.format;
        document.getElementById("checkoutPrice").textContent = offerData.price;
        document.getElementById("checkoutOutcome").textContent = offerData.outcome;
        document.getElementById("checkoutNextSteps").textContent = offerData.nextSteps;
        checkoutSupport.dataset.message = offerData.whatsappMessage;
        leadInterest.textContent = offerData.name;
        checkoutStatus.classList.add("hidden");
        checkoutStatus.textContent = "";

        const methodsContainer = document.getElementById("checkoutMethods");
        methodsContainer.innerHTML = "";
        offerData.paymentMethods.forEach((method) => {
          const chip = document.createElement("span");
          chip.className = "rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-slate-600";
          chip.textContent = method;
          methodsContainer.appendChild(chip);
        });

        const primaryLabels = {
          hosted: "Proceed to Secure Checkout",
          reserve: "Reserve / Continue",
          whatsapp: "Request on WhatsApp",
          apply: "Apply on WhatsApp"
        };

        checkoutPrimary.textContent = primaryLabels[offerData.paymentType] || "Continue";
        modal.classList.remove("hidden");
        document.body.classList.add("no-scroll");
        wireContactLinks();
      }

      function closeCheckout() {
        modal.classList.add("hidden");
        document.body.classList.remove("no-scroll");
      }

      document.querySelectorAll("[data-open-offer]").forEach((button) => {
        button.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
          event.preventDefault();
          const offerData = {
            name: button.dataset.offerName,
            price: button.dataset.price,
            format: button.dataset.format,
            for: button.dataset.for,
            outcome: button.dataset.outcome,
            paymentLink: button.dataset.paymentLink,
            paymentType: button.dataset.paymentType,
            whatsappMessage: button.dataset.whatsappMessage,
            nextSteps: button.dataset.nextSteps,
            paymentMethods: (button.dataset.paymentMethods || "").split("|").filter(Boolean)
          };

          openCheckout(offerData);
        });
      });

      document.querySelectorAll("[data-close-checkout]").forEach((element) => {
        element.addEventListener("click", closeCheckout);
      });

      document.addEventListener("keydown", (event) => {
        if (event.key === "Escape" && !modal.classList.contains("hidden")) {
          closeCheckout();
        }
      });

      checkoutPrimary.addEventListener("click", () => {
        if (!state.currentOffer) return;

        const offer = state.currentOffer;
        const whatsappUrl = buildWhatsAppUrl(offer.whatsappMessage);

        if (offer.paymentType === "hosted") {
          if (/^https?:\/\//i.test(offer.paymentLink)) {
            window.open(offer.paymentLink, "_blank", "noopener,noreferrer");
            return;
          }
          checkoutStatus.textContent = "This checkout link is not configured yet. Add the relevant PAYMENT_LINK_* value in .env or continue on WhatsApp below.";
          checkoutStatus.classList.remove("hidden");
          return;
        }

        if (offer.paymentType === "reserve" || offer.paymentType === "whatsapp" || offer.paymentType === "apply") {
          if (whatsappUrl) {
            window.open(whatsappUrl, "_blank", "noopener,noreferrer");
          } else {
            checkoutStatus.textContent = "WhatsApp is not configured yet. Add BRAND_WHATSAPP_NUMBER in .env to activate this action.";
            checkoutStatus.classList.remove("hidden");
          }
        }
      });

      function validateLeadForm() {
        const name = leadName.value.trim();
        const email = leadEmail.value.trim();
        const validEmail = /^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$/.test(email);

        const nameValid = name.length > 1;
        const emailValid = validEmail;

        nameError.classList.toggle("hidden", nameValid);
        emailError.classList.toggle("hidden", emailValid);
        leadName.setAttribute("aria-invalid", String(!nameValid));
        leadEmail.setAttribute("aria-invalid", String(!emailValid));

        return nameValid && emailValid;
      }

      leadForm.addEventListener("submit", (event) => {
        event.preventDefault();

        if (!validateLeadForm()) {
          showToast("Please complete the form before submitting.");
          return;
        }

        leadSubmit.disabled = true;
        leadSubmit.textContent = "Submitting...";
        leadState.classList.remove("hidden");
        leadState.className = "mt-5 rounded-[24px] border border-white/10 bg-white/10 px-5 py-4 text-white";
        leadState.textContent = "Submitting your details for follow-up.";

        const payload = {
          name: leadName.value.trim(),
          email: leadEmail.value.trim(),
          interest: leadInterest.textContent,
          source: "website"
        };

        fetch(SITE_CONFIG.leadCaptureEndpoint, {
          method: "POST",
          headers: {
            "Content-Type": "application/json",
            "Accept": "application/json",
            "X-CSRF-TOKEN": document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]').getAttribute("content")
          },
          body: JSON.stringify(payload)
        })
          .then(async (response) => {
            const data = await response.json().catch(() => ({}));

            if (!response.ok) {
              throw { status: response.status, data };
            }

            return data;
          })
          .then((data) => {
            leadSubmit.disabled = false;
            leadSubmit.textContent = "Request Follow-Up";
            leadState.className = "mt-5 rounded-[24px] bg-white px-5 py-4 text-slate-900";
            leadState.innerHTML =
              "<p class=\"text-base font-semibold text-ink\">" + (data.message || SITE_CONFIG.leadSuccessMessage) + "</p>" +
              "<p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">Your interest has been captured in Laravel, so follow-up can now continue through a real backend flow. For faster support, continue on WhatsApp now.</p>" +
              "<a href=\"#\" data-wa-link data-message=\"Habari Paul, nimetuma details zangu kwenye website yako na naomba unifuatilie.\" class=\"mt-4 inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center rounded-full bg-whatsapp px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Continue on WhatsApp</a>";
            wireContactLinks();
            leadForm.reset();
            leadInterest.textContent = "General inquiry";
          })
          .catch((error) => {
            leadSubmit.disabled = false;
            leadSubmit.textContent = "Request Follow-Up";

            const errors = error?.data?.errors || {};
            const firstError = Object.values(errors).flat()[0];

            leadState.className = "mt-5 rounded-[24px] border border-red-200 bg-red-50 px-5 py-4 text-red-900";
            leadState.textContent = firstError || "We could not submit your request right now. Please try again or continue on WhatsApp.";

            nameError.classList.toggle("hidden", !errors.name);
            emailError.classList.toggle("hidden", !errors.email);
          });
      });

      // ── Video Lightbox ──────────────────────────────────
      (function () {
        const lightbox = document.getElementById('videoLightbox');
        const lbVideo  = document.getElementById('lbVideo');
        const lbTitle  = document.getElementById('lbTitle');
        const lbClose  = document.getElementById('lbClose');

        function openLightbox(src, title) {
          lbVideo.src = src;
          lbTitle.textContent = title || '';
          lightbox.classList.add('open');
          document.body.classList.add('no-scroll');
          lbVideo.play().catch(() => {});
        }

        function closeLightbox() {
          lightbox.classList.remove('open');
          document.body.classList.remove('no-scroll');
          lbVideo.pause();
          lbVideo.src = '';
        }

        document.querySelectorAll('.video-card').forEach(function (card) {
          function activate() {
            openLightbox(card.dataset.videoSrc, card.dataset.videoTitle);
          }
          card.addEventListener('click', activate);
          card.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
            if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') { e.preventDefault(); activate(); }
          });
        });

        lbClose.addEventListener('click', closeLightbox);
        lightbox.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
          if (e.target === lightbox) closeLightbox();
        });
        document.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
          if (e.key === 'Escape' && lightbox.classList.contains('open')) closeLightbox();
        });
      })();

      wireContactLinks();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
